  /* ══════════════════════════════════════════
     THE ONLY ELEMENT THAT HAS HEIGHT.
     Everything else is position:fixed or
     position:absolute inside this.
     Total = S1(400vh) + S2(400vh) + S3(400vh)
           = 1200vh. No gaps possible.
  ══════════════════════════════════════════ */
